{
  "title": "Episode 1: The Crash Landing（硬着陆）",
  "steps": [
    {
      "type": "narrator",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "avatar": "/assets/NPC.png",
      "text": "搬进4B，走廊箱子摔了，Mrs. Henderson和Jake帮你搬东西。暖气不热，Jake帮修。",
      "text_cn": "（搬进4B，走廊箱子摔了，Mrs. Henderson和Jake帮你搬东西。暖气不热，Jake帮修。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "narrator",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "avatar": "/assets/NPC.png",
      "text": "You just arrived in America alone. Your partner is still overseas. You're moving into apartment 4B — and your boxes just crashed in the hallway.",
      "text_cn": "（你独自来到美国。伴侣还在国内。你正搬进4B公寓——箱子在走廊摔了一地。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "narrator",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "avatar": "/assets/NPC.png",
      "text": "你拖着箱子走进走廊，箱子摔了。Mrs. Henderson打开门。",
      "text_cn": "（你拖着箱子走进走廊，箱子摔了。Mrs. Henderson打开门。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Mrs. Henderson",
      "avatar": "/assets/MrsHendersonhappy.png",
      "text": "Oh! Are you okay?",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "You",
      "avatar": "/assets/yousorrow.png",
      "text": "Yes, I'm okay. Sorry... the noise...",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Mrs. Henderson",
      "avatar": "/assets/MrsHendersonsorrow.png",
      "text": "Don't worry! Are you the new neighbor? 4B?",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "You",
      "avatar": "/assets/youhappy.png",
      "text": "Yes. I'm moving in today.",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Mrs. Henderson",
      "avatar": "/assets/MrsHendersonhappy.png",
      "text": "Welcome! I'm Mrs. Henderson. 4A. Right next door.",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "format": "multiple_choice",
      "instruction": "📍 题目1\n\"Moving in\" means:",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "text": "来到新家住",
          "is_correct": true
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "text": "离开这里",
          "is_correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "text": "在里面走动",
          "is_correct": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narrator",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "avatar": "/assets/NPC.png",
      "text": "Jake从楼上跑下来。",
      "text_cn": "（Jake从楼上跑下来。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Jake",
      "avatar": "/assets/jackhappy.png",
      "text": "Hey! Do you need help?",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "format": "multiple_choice",
      "instruction": "📍 题目2\nJake asks \"Do you need help?\" You want to say yes. What do you say?",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "text": "\"No, go away.\"",
          "is_correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "text": "\"Yes, please!\"",
          "is_correct": true
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "text": "\"I don't know you.\"",
          "is_correct": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narrator",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "avatar": "/assets/NPC.png",
      "text": "Jake is right above you — in 5B. He talks fast, but he's friendly.",
      "text_cn": "（Jake就住你正楼上——5B。他说话很快，但人很友好。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "narrator",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "avatar": "/assets/NPC.png",
      "text": "三个人把箱子搬进4B。",
      "text_cn": "（三个人把箱子搬进4B。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "You",
      "avatar": "/assets/youhappy.png",
      "text": "Yes, please!",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Jake",
      "avatar": "/assets/jackhappy.png",
      "text": "I'm Jake. 5B. Upstairs.",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "You",
      "avatar": "/assets/youhappy.png",
      "text": "Nice to meet you.",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Mrs. Henderson",
      "avatar": "/assets/MrsHendersonanger.png",
      "text": "Here — cookies! I made them today. For you!",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "format": "multiple_choice",
      "instruction": "📍 题目3\nMrs. Henderson gives you cookies as a welcome gift. What's the best response?",
      "options": [
        {
          "label": "A",
          "text": "\"No, no, I can't take this.\"",
          "is_correct": false
        },
        {
          "label": "B",
          "text": "\"Thank you so much!\"",
          "is_correct": true
        },
        {
          "label": "C",
          "text": "\"How much do I pay?\"",
          "is_correct": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "narrator",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "avatar": "/assets/NPC.png",
      "text": "You take the cookies. They smell sweet and warm. Then, when you step inside your new apartment, you notice something else — it's cold.",
      "text_cn": "（你接过饼干。它们闻起来又甜又暖。可当你走进新公寓时，又注意到另一件事——里面很冷。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "narrator",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "avatar": "/assets/NPC.png",
      "text": "你进了公寓，发现很冷。",
      "text_cn": "（你进了公寓，发现很冷。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "narrator",
      "speaker": "旁白",
      "avatar": "/assets/NPC.png",
      "text": "Jake弄好了。",
      "text_cn": "（Jake弄好了。）"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "You",
      "avatar": "/assets/youhappiness.png",
      "text": "Thank you so much!",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Jake",
      "avatar": "/assets/jackhappy.png",
      "text": "Mrs. H makes the best cookies. You owe me dinner now. Just kidding!",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "You",
      "avatar": "/assets/youhappy.png",
      "text": "It's cold in here...",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Jake",
      "avatar": "/assets/jackhappy.png",
      "text": "Oh — the heater is off. Let me fix it.",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speaker": "Jake",
      "avatar": "/assets/jackhappy.png",
      "text": "Done. It'll be warm soon.",
      "text_cn": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "question",
      "format": "matching",
      "instruction": "📍 题目4\nMatch the English words with their meanings:",
      "pairs": [
